8. You are designing a website for a University. It has hundreds of pages (Admissions,
Departments, Alumni, News). Which structural model would you choose? Draw a rough
diagram and justify your choice.
Recommended Structural Model: Hierarchical (Tree) Structure

Justification:
	•	A university website has large and diverse content (Admissions, Departments, Alumni, News).
	•	Hierarchical structure allows categorization of information into main sections and sub-sections.
	•	Users can navigate easily to the section they need without following a strict sequence.
	•	It is scalable, allowing the addition of new departments, events, or news without reorganizing the entire site.
Homepage
